{
  "stem": "1042.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was more than one day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was two days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they couldn't kill all of them in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were prepared with the big trucks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to send them to Auschwitz, and to Bergen-Belsen, to other places, you know, where they used to kill the people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So not exactly all of them were killed there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they send out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this-- everything we-- those working people, they knew about that we-- we had, again, some papers from the Army that we are needed still.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we presume that the end will be that they're going to kill us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then after the ghetto, they start to build concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So also the concentration camp was not far from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They built on Jewish cemeteries.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was two big cemeteries, because Krakow was like two cities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was-- and the Vistula was a bridge, was on the other side, that was Krakow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the other side from the Vistula after the bridge was [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Podwoloczyska. ?] So I used to live in [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Podwoloczyska. ?] So then they start to build the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They throw out all the people what were, you know, in the graves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my people, my parents, were buried in the same cemetery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when I-- they start to build the barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was working on the barracks, too, there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I knew where my parents were buried, where we built the barrack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I knew that I am on the place where my parents were buried there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was there in the camp for two years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like I-- you know, I-- I had in my mind that I am living with my parents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, that was, the barrack was built on the graves.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
